%div{class: 'modal fade', id: 'modal-remote-config'}
  %div{class: 'modal-dialog'}
    %div{class: 'modal-content'}
      %div{class: 'modal-header text-center'} 
        %h4 Online Profile Settings
      %div{class: 'modal-body'}
        %div{class: 'row'}
          %div{class: 'col-xs-4'}
            %h4 Friendly Name
          %div{class: 'col-xs-8'}
            %h4
              %span{id: 'remote-friendly-name'} Friendly Name
          %div{class: 'col-xs-12 text-muted'}
            This name is what your friends will see when you share your profile and also how they will find you
            
        %div{class: 'row'}
        %h4 Shared Profiles
        %hr
        %div{id: 'sharing-settings', class: 'row'}
          / %div{class: 'col-xs-4'}
          /   %h4 A
          / %div{class: 'col-xs-8'}
          /   %div{class: 'col-xs-8 input-group input-group-sm share-cell', 'data-profile-name': 'default'}
          /     %input{type: 'text', class: 'form-control survivor-typeahead'}
          /     %h5 
          /       %span{class: 'glyphicon glyphicon-share profile-shared'}
          /     %h5
          /       %span{class: 'glyphicon glyphicon-remove profile-unshare'}
      %div{class: 'modal-footer'}
        %button{type: 'button', class: 'btn btn-default', 'data-dismiss': 'modal'} Close